ARTICLES.push({slug:"how-much-do-igaming-affiliates-earn",title:"How Much Do iGaming Affiliates Earn in 2026?",desc:"A realistic look at how much iGaming affiliates earn in 2026, what drives the range from beginner to top earner, and how commission models affect income.",h1:"How Much Do iGaming Affiliates Earn?",intro:"Affiliate income varies enormously, from pocket money to six figures a month. This guide gives a realistic picture of the range and what drives it. The commission options behind those numbers sit in the DBBET <a href=\"/partner-benefits/\" style=\"color:#ff3b6b\">partner benefits</a>.",sections:[{h2:"The honest income range",paras:["Most beginners earn little for the first months while they learn. Mid-level affiliates can earn steady part-time income, and top performers reach five or six figures monthly.","The difference is rarely talent alone; it is niche selection, traffic quality, consistency and commission structure compounding over time."],subs:[{h3:"What different earners make",paras:["Most beginners earn little in the first months while they learn, mid-level affiliates earn a steady part-time income, and top performers reach five or six figures monthly."]},{h3:"What separates the tiers",paras:["The difference is rarely talent alone; it is niche selection, traffic quality, consistency and commission structure compounding over time."]}]},{h2:"What drives the numbers",paras:["RevShare income grows with the lifetime value of your players, so retention and GEO quality matter more than raw clicks.","CPA and hybrid deals reward volume and let you bank value faster. Choosing the right model for your traffic can multiply the same audience's income."]},{h2:"How to grow into the higher range",paras:["Treat the first 90 days as learning, not earning. Track everything, double down on what converts, and reinvest profits to scale.","With up to 55% RevShare, a $110 CPA option and 24/7 support, DBBET Partners gives affiliates room to grow into the higher end of the range."]}],keys:["Income spans from near zero for beginners to six figures for top earners","Niche, traffic quality and consistency drive the difference, not luck","Matching the commission model to your traffic can multiply earnings"],related:[{href:"/blog/affiliate-income-success-stories/",text:"Success story patterns"},{href:"/blog/your-first-1000-affiliate-income/",text:"Your first $1000"}]});
ARTICLES.push({slug:"your-first-1000-affiliate-income",title:"How to Earn Your First $1000 in Affiliate Income (2026)",desc:"A practical roadmap to your first $1000 in iGaming affiliate income in 2026: pick a niche, create content, drive traffic and convert.",h1:"How to Earn Your First $1000 in Affiliate Income",intro:"The first $1000 is the hardest and the most important milestone. It proves your system works. This roadmap shows the steps that get you there. The program tools you will use are in the DBBET <a href=\"/partner-benefits/\" style=\"color:#ff3b6b\">partner benefits</a>.",sections:[{h2:"Pick a focused niche and offer",paras:["Choose one GEO or player type you understand, and one strong program to promote. Focus beats spreading thin when you are starting.","A flexible program lets you test RevShare versus CPA on the same traffic so you can see which path reaches $1000 faster."],subs:[{h3:"Choose one GEO and offer",paras:["Choose one GEO or player type you understand and one strong program to promote, because focus beats spreading thin when you are starting out."]},{h3:"Stay flexible on the model",paras:["A flexible program lets you test RevShare versus CPA on the same traffic so you can see which path reaches $1000 faster."]}]},{h2:"Create content that converts",paras:["Answer the real questions your audience asks before they sign up: which program, how to join, how payouts work. Honest, useful content earns trust and clicks.","Place clear, soft calls to action near the top, middle and end of each page so interested readers can act without friction."]},{h2:"Drive and optimise traffic",paras:["Start with one channel you can do well, whether SEO, social or a niche community. Track which pages and sources convert, then double down.","Once you hit your first qualified players, lean on 24/7 support to optimise offers and push past $1000 towards a repeatable system."]}],keys:["Focus on one niche and one strong program to reach the first milestone","Useful, honest content with clear soft CTAs converts best","Master one traffic channel, track results, then double down"],related:[{href:"/blog/how-to-join-igaming-affiliate-program/",text:"How to join"},{href:"/blog/scaling-affiliate-business/",text:"Scaling up"}]});
ARTICLES.push({slug:"scaling-affiliate-business",title:"Scaling an iGaming Affiliate Business in 2026",desc:"How to scale an iGaming affiliate business in 2026: systemise content, expand GEOs, add traffic channels and use sub-affiliates to grow income.",h1:"Scaling Your iGaming Affiliate Business",intro:"Once you are earning consistently, scaling is about systems, not just effort. This guide covers how to grow income without burning out. The multiple income streams you will lean on are in the DBBET <a href=\"/partner-benefits/\" style=\"color:#ff3b6b\">partner benefits</a>.",sections:[{h2:"Systemise what already works",paras:["Document the content and campaigns that convert, then templatise them so you can repeat the formula across new topics and GEOs.","Systems let you delegate or outsource, freeing your time for strategy rather than repetitive production."],subs:[{h3:"Document what converts",paras:["Document the content and campaigns that already convert, then templatise them so you can repeat the formula across new topics and GEOs."]},{h3:"Delegate the repeatable work",paras:["Systems let you delegate or outsource production, freeing your time for strategy rather than repetitive production."]}]},{h2:"Expand GEOs and channels",paras:["Add adjacent GEOs where your winning content can be localised, and layer in new traffic channels one at a time so you can measure each.","DBBET Partners' coverage of Africa, Asia and the Middle East gives you fresh, high-growth markets to expand into with localised products."]},{h2:"Add sub-affiliate income",paras:["As you build authority, recruit other affiliates and earn 10% sub-affiliate income on their results, creating a near-passive layer on top of your direct earnings.","Combined with RevShare, CPA and hybrid deals, this turns a solo operation into a diversified affiliate business."]}],keys:["Systemise winning content so it can be repeated and delegated","Expand into adjacent GEOs and add channels one at a time","Sub-affiliate income adds a near-passive layer on top of direct earnings"],related:[{href:"/blog/sub-affiliate-programs/",text:"Sub-affiliate programs"},{href:"/blog/passive-income-affiliate-marketing/",text:"Passive income"}]});
ARTICLES.push({slug:"passive-income-affiliate-marketing",title:"Passive Income With iGaming Affiliate Marketing (2026)",desc:"How iGaming affiliate marketing can build passive income in 2026 through RevShare and sub-affiliates, and what passive really means in practice.",h1:"Building Passive Income With Affiliate Marketing",intro:"Affiliate income can become genuinely passive, but only after the upfront work is done. This guide explains how to get there honestly. The recurring income models that make it possible are in the DBBET <a href=\"/partner-benefits/\" style=\"color:#ff3b6b\">partner benefits</a>.",sections:[{h2:"What passive income really means",paras:["Truly passive income still needs occasional maintenance. The goal is income that keeps arriving from work you already did, not zero effort forever.","RevShare is the engine of passive affiliate income: players you referred months ago keep generating commissions while you focus on new content."],subs:[{h3:"Passive is not zero effort",paras:["Truly passive income still needs occasional maintenance. The goal is income that keeps arriving from work you already did, not zero effort forever."]},{h3:"RevShare is the engine",paras:["RevShare is the engine of passive affiliate income: players you referred months ago keep generating commissions while you focus on new content."]}]},{h2:"Assets that keep paying",paras:["Evergreen content that ranks, email lists you own, and loyal player bases all keep producing income long after creation.","The more your assets compound, the less each new dollar depends on fresh daily effort."]},{h2:"Adding a sub-affiliate layer",paras:["Recruiting sub-affiliates adds a second passive stream: you earn 10% of their results without sending traffic yourself.","Combining evergreen RevShare content with sub-affiliate income is how many affiliates build durable, semi-passive businesses through DBBET Partners."]}],keys:["Passive income still needs occasional maintenance, not zero effort","RevShare and evergreen content keep paying from past work","A 10% sub-affiliate layer adds a second semi-passive income stream"],related:[{href:"/blog/revshare-explained/",text:"RevShare explained"},{href:"/blog/sub-affiliate-programs/",text:"Sub-affiliate programs"}]});
ARTICLES.push({slug:"common-affiliate-marketing-mistakes",title:"Common iGaming Affiliate Marketing Mistakes (2026)",desc:"The most common iGaming affiliate marketing mistakes in 2026 and how to avoid them, from chasing rates to ignoring compliance and tracking.",h1:"Common Affiliate Marketing Mistakes to Avoid",intro:"Most affiliates fail for the same avoidable reasons. Knowing the traps in advance saves you months of wasted effort. Picking a solid program is the first defence, so review the DBBET <a href=\"/partner-benefits/\" style=\"color:#ff3b6b\">partner benefits</a>.",sections:[{h2:"Chasing rates over real earnings",paras:["The biggest mistake is picking a program for its headline rate while ignoring product quality, retention and payout reliability.","A slightly lower rate on a brand players love and that pays on time usually out-earns a flashy number you struggle to collect."],subs:[{h3:"Why the headline rate fools you",paras:["The biggest mistake is picking a program for its headline rate while ignoring product quality, retention and payout reliability."]},{h3:"What actually pays more",paras:["A slightly lower rate on a brand players love and that pays on time usually out-earns a flashy number you struggle to collect."]}]},{h2:"Ignoring compliance and terms",paras:["Sending incentivised traffic, breaching GEO rules or using banned methods leads to clawbacks and bans. Read the terms before you scale.","Compliance is not bureaucracy; it protects the income you have already earned from being reversed."]},{h2:"Neglecting tracking and testing",paras:["Affiliates who do not track which pages, sources and offers convert are flying blind. Without data you cannot improve.","Set up clean tracking, test systematically, and lean on 24/7 support to fix issues fast before they cost you players."]}],keys:["Do not chase headline rates over real, collectable earnings","Respect compliance and program terms to protect your income","Track and test everything; data is what turns effort into growth"],related:[{href:"/blog/affiliate-marketing-compliance/",text:"Compliance guide"},{href:"/blog/affiliate-programs-for-beginners/",text:"Programs for beginners"}]});
