ARTICLES.push({slug:"russian-affiliate-programs-2026",title:"Russian Affiliate Programs 2026: CIS iGaming Guide",desc:"A 2026 guide to iGaming affiliate marketing for Russia and the CIS: localisation, payments and converting this audience. Learn how to get started.",h1:"Russian and CIS Affiliate Programs 2026",intro:"Russia and the wider CIS region remain a large, engaged iGaming audience. Affiliates who localise into Russian can tap a substantial market. DBBET Partners supports Russian-language traffic, as shown in its <a href=\"/partner-benefits/\" style=\"color:#ff3b6b\">partner benefits</a>.",sections:[{h2:"The CIS audience opportunity",paras:["Russian-speaking audiences span many countries and share a common language, letting one well-localised site reach a broad market.","Sports and casino engagement is high, and players respond well to content that speaks their language and references familiar competitions."],subs:[{h3:"A large Russian-speaking market",paras:["Russian-speaking audiences span many countries and share a common language, letting one well-localised site reach a broad market."]},{h3:"Strong sports and casino demand",paras:["Sports and casino engagement is high, and players respond well to content that speaks their language and references familiar competitions."]}]},{h2:"Localising for Russian speakers",paras:["High-quality Russian content, local payment methods and culturally relevant promotions are essential for trust and conversion.","Promote brands that genuinely support the region. DBBET Partners offers Russian-language products that help your traffic convert."]},{h2:"Converting CIS traffic",paras:["Focus on the questions and sports your audience cares about, and provide clear, soft calls to action throughout your content.","Use flexible RevShare, CPA and hybrid deals plus 24/7 support to optimise for how CIS players actually behave."]}],keys:["A common Russian language lets one site reach many CIS countries","Russian localisation and local payments are essential for conversion","Flexible commission models help you optimise for CIS player behaviour"],related:[{href:"/blog/tier-1-vs-tier-3-affiliate-traffic/",text:"Tier-1 vs tier-3 traffic"},{href:"/blog/european-affiliate-programs-compliance/",text:"European programs and compliance"}]});
ARTICLES.push({slug:"latin-american-affiliate-programs",title:"Latin American Affiliate Programs: 2026 iGaming Guide",desc:"Succeed with iGaming affiliate marketing in Latin America: Brazil, Spanish markets, localisation and football culture. See the playbook and apply now.",h1:"Latin American Affiliate Programs",intro:"Latin America is booming for iGaming, led by Brazil and a wave of Spanish-speaking markets. Affiliates who localise well can grow fast here. DBBET Partners supports the region, as shown in its <a href=\"/partner-benefits/\" style=\"color:#ff3b6b\">partner benefits</a>.",sections:[{h2:"Why Latin America is growing",paras:["Regulation is opening up, smartphone use is high, and football passion drives huge betting engagement across Brazil and Spanish-speaking countries.","Many markets are still early, so affiliates who establish trusted content now can build durable, compounding traffic."],subs:[{h3:"Brazil leads the growth",paras:["Regulation is opening up, smartphone use is high, and football passion drives huge betting engagement across Brazil and Spanish-speaking countries."]},{h3:"Early markets reward first movers",paras:["Many markets are still early, so affiliates who establish trusted content now can build durable, compounding traffic."]}]},{h2:"Portuguese and Spanish localisation",paras:["Brazil needs Portuguese content, while much of the rest of the region needs Spanish. Football-led angles and local payment methods convert best.","Promote brands that support local currencies and payments so your referred players can deposit easily and stick around."]},{h2:"Building a LatAm strategy",paras:["Start with Brazil or one Spanish-speaking country, build football-focused content, and expand once you have a converting model.","DBBET Partners offers multilingual support and flexible RevShare, CPA and hybrid deals to monetise LatAm traffic effectively."]}],keys:["Brazil and Spanish-speaking markets are growing fast for iGaming","Portuguese or Spanish localisation plus football angles convert best","Start with one market, then expand the winning football-led formula"],related:[{href:"/blog/tier-1-vs-tier-3-affiliate-traffic/",text:"Tier-1 vs tier-3 traffic"},{href:"/blog/igaming-affiliate-programs-asia/",text:"Programs in Asia"}]});
ARTICLES.push({slug:"european-affiliate-programs-compliance",title:"European Affiliate Programs & Compliance (2026)",desc:"How European iGaming affiliate programs work in 2026, why compliance and licensing matter, and how to promote responsibly across regulated EU markets.",h1:"European Affiliate Programs and Compliance",intro:"Europe is a mature, heavily regulated iGaming market where compliance is as important as commission. This guide explains how to operate responsibly. Review program terms in the DBBET <a href=\"/partner-benefits/\" style=\"color:#ff3b6b\">partner benefits</a>.",sections:[{h2:"A regulated, mature market",paras:["European markets are competitive and well-regulated, with licensing rules that vary by country. Player value can be high, but so are standards.","Success here comes from trust and authority rather than aggressive tactics, which regulators and players both reject."],subs:[{h3:"High value, high standards",paras:["European markets are competitive and well-regulated, with licensing rules that vary by country. Player value can be high, but so are standards."]},{h3:"Trust beats aggressive tactics",paras:["Success here comes from trust and authority rather than aggressive tactics, which regulators and players both reject."]}]},{h2:"Why compliance matters most",paras:["Each market has its own licensing and advertising rules. Promoting without respecting them risks penalties and account loss.","Always follow local regulations, include responsible-gambling messaging, and only target permitted regions and ages."]},{h2:"Promoting responsibly in Europe",paras:["Lead with honest, high-quality content and clear responsible-gambling notices. This builds the trust that converts in mature markets.","DBBET Partners supports compliant promotion with clear terms and 24/7 support, so you can operate confidently within the rules."]}],keys:["Europe is mature, competitive and heavily regulated","Compliance and licensing rules vary by country and must be respected","Trust, authority and responsible messaging win in mature markets"],related:[{href:"/blog/affiliate-marketing-compliance/",text:"Compliance guide"},{href:"/blog/common-affiliate-marketing-mistakes/",text:"Common mistakes"}]});
ARTICLES.push({slug:"affiliate-fraud-prevention",title:"Affiliate Fraud Prevention: Protect Your Earnings (2026)",desc:"How affiliate fraud works in iGaming, why it threatens your account and earnings, and practical steps to keep your traffic clean in 2026.",h1:"Affiliate Fraud Prevention for iGaming Affiliates",intro:"Fraud is the fastest way to lose an affiliate account and clawed-back earnings. Understanding and preventing it protects your business. Programs value clean traffic, as reflected in the DBBET <a href=\"/partner-benefits/\" style=\"color:#ff3b6b\">partner benefits</a>.",sections:[{h2:"What counts as affiliate fraud",paras:["Fraud includes incentivised sign-ups, bot traffic, self-referrals, fake accounts and misleading promotions. All of it harms operators and gets affiliates banned.","Even unintentional issues, like buying low-quality traffic, can look like fraud to detection systems and trigger reviews."],subs:[{h3:"The obvious red flags",paras:["Fraud includes incentivised sign-ups, bot traffic, self-referrals, fake accounts and misleading promotions. All of it harms operators and gets affiliates banned."]},{h3:"The accidental ones too",paras:["Even unintentional issues, like buying low-quality traffic, can look like fraud to detection systems and trigger reviews."]}]},{h2:"Why clean traffic pays better",paras:["Operators reward affiliates who send genuine, converting players with better terms and faster payouts.","Clean traffic also protects your lifetime RevShare, since real players keep playing while fake ones get removed and reversed."]},{h2:"Practical fraud prevention",paras:["Vet your traffic sources, avoid incentivised methods, monitor your analytics for anomalies, and follow each program's terms closely.","Lean on 24/7 support to flag and resolve suspicious patterns early, before they put your account at risk."]}],keys:["Fraud includes incentivised, bot, self-referral and fake-account traffic","Clean traffic earns better terms, faster payouts and protected RevShare","Vet sources, monitor analytics and follow program terms to stay safe"],related:[{href:"/blog/affiliate-marketing-compliance/",text:"Compliance guide"},{href:"/blog/common-affiliate-marketing-mistakes/",text:"Common mistakes"}]});
ARTICLES.push({slug:"affiliate-marketing-compliance",title:"Affiliate Marketing Compliance in iGaming (2026)",desc:"A practical guide to iGaming affiliate marketing compliance in 2026: licensing, advertising rules, responsible gambling and protecting your account.",h1:"Affiliate Marketing Compliance: A Practical Guide",intro:"Compliance is what keeps your affiliate income safe and your account open. This guide covers the essentials every iGaming affiliate should follow. Solid program terms make compliance easier, as shown in the DBBET <a href=\"/partner-benefits/\" style=\"color:#ff3b6b\">partner benefits</a>.",sections:[{h2:"Know the rules that apply to you",paras:["Advertising rules, age restrictions and licensing requirements differ by country. You are responsible for promoting only where and how you are permitted.","Read each program's terms and the local regulations for every GEO you target before you scale traffic there."],subs:[{h3:"Rules differ by country",paras:["Advertising rules, age restrictions and licensing requirements differ by country. You are responsible for promoting only where and how you are permitted."]},{h3:"Check terms before you scale",paras:["Read each program's terms and the local regulations for every GEO you target before you scale traffic there."]}]},{h2:"Responsible gambling messaging",paras:["Include clear 18+ and responsible-gambling notices, and never use language that pressures vulnerable people or hides risk.","Responsible promotion is both an ethical duty and a practical one, since regulators and operators penalise the alternative."]},{h2:"Protecting your account",paras:["Keep records of your traffic sources and creatives, avoid prohibited methods, and respond quickly to any program queries.","DBBET Partners provides clear terms and 24/7 support, so you can confirm what is allowed and stay compliant as you grow."]}],keys:["Advertising, age and licensing rules vary by country and bind you","Always include 18+ and responsible-gambling messaging","Keep records, avoid prohibited methods and respond to program queries"],related:[{href:"/blog/affiliate-fraud-prevention/",text:"Fraud prevention"},{href:"/blog/european-affiliate-programs-compliance/",text:"European compliance"}]});
ARTICLES.push({slug:"affiliate-marketing-roi-guide",title:"The Complete Guide to Affiliate Marketing ROI (2026)",desc:"How to measure and improve affiliate marketing ROI in 2026: tracking net income per click, attribution, and optimising spend across GEOs and channels.",h1:"The Complete Guide to Affiliate Marketing ROI",intro:"ROI is the number that decides whether your affiliate business grows or stalls. This guide shows how to measure and improve it properly. The commission models that drive ROI are in the DBBET <a href=\"/partner-benefits/\" style=\"color:#ff3b6b\">partner benefits</a>.",sections:[{h2:"Measuring ROI the right way",paras:["True ROI compares all costs, including time, content and paid traffic, against net commissions actually received, not headline rates.","Track net income per click by source and GEO so you can see exactly which efforts pay and which drain your budget."],subs:[{h3:"Count every cost",paras:["True ROI compares all costs, including time, content and paid traffic, against net commissions actually received."]},{h3:"Track by source and GEO",paras:["Track net income per click by source and GEO so you can see exactly which efforts pay and which drain your budget."]}]},{h2:"Improving ROI across channels",paras:["Cut or fix underperforming sources, double down on winners, and test new creatives systematically rather than randomly.","RevShare improves ROI over time as referred players keep paying, so factor lifetime value into your calculations, not just first deposits."]},{h2:"Scaling profitably",paras:["Only scale channels with proven positive ROI, and reinvest profits gradually so you can react if performance shifts.","With flexible RevShare, CPA and hybrid options plus 24/7 support, DBBET Partners lets you optimise ROI per campaign and GEO."]}],keys:["True ROI counts all costs against net commissions actually received","Track net income per click by source and GEO to find real winners","Factor RevShare lifetime value into ROI, not just first deposits"],related:[{href:"/blog/highest-paying-affiliate-programs/",text:"Highest paying programs"},{href:"/blog/traffic-sources-for-affiliates/",text:"Traffic sources"}]});
